name: composite_cyce
jaxpr:
{ lambda ; a:f32[2,6]. let
    b:f32[2,6] = abs a
    c:f32[2,6] = neg b
    d:f32[2,6] = exp c
    e:f32[2,6] = custom_jvp_call[
      name=relu
      call_jaxpr={ lambda ; f:f32[2,6]. let
          g:f32[2,6] = jit[
            name=relu
            jaxpr={ lambda ; f:f32[2,6]. let
                g:f32[2,6] = max f 0.0:f32[]
              in (g,) }
          ] f
        in (g,) }
      jvp=jvp
      symbolic_zeros=False
    ] a
    h:f32[2,6] = add d e
  in (h,) }
